<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-1912] DefaultCamelContext.removeEndpoints() fails due to ConcurrentModificationException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-1912</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The removeEndpoints() method iterates over the endpoints map, and attempts to remove entries inside of the iterator loop.  This causes near immediate ConcurrentModificationException&apos;s.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12487146">CAMEL-1912</key>
