                            <comment id="12952005" author="erh" created="Fri, 14 Aug 2009 20:19:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a patch against the current version of /trunk/camel-core/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/impl/DefaultCamelContext.java (r800180) that should fix the problem&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12951864" author="davsclaus" created="Sat, 15 Aug 2009 06:30:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for contributing. Will get it in the next release after 2.0 as 2.0 is currently being build.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would suggest to use a Collections.unmodifiedList wrapper instead of copying to new array in the first 1-2 methods.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And the code in the remove could use generics instead of the type cast and it should comply with the checkstyle&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;b&gt;building with checkstyle&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
